packages.Rmd

List of packages included in twinetverse.

rtweet

rtweet is an R client for accessing Twitter’s REST and stream APIs. Check out the thorough documentation website.

graphTweets

graphTweets is an R package to visualise Twitter conversations. Check the website for examples and documentation.

sigmajs

sigmajs lets you visualise social network in a highly configurable and interactive way. Check the website for examples and complete documentation.
